Question 13Answer

a.
\frac{\sqrt{2-x}-x}{3-2\sqrt{2-x}}


b.
\frac{\sqrt{2}+\sqrt{x}}{6\sqrt{2-x}}


c.
\frac{5-4x}{6\sqrt{2-x}}


d.
\frac{4-5x}{6\sqrt{2-x}}


e.
1-x

